node.text:
How to get the keys. She takes a car to the Roosevelt hotel. Her driver will tell her the secrets of the place and how to get to the rooftop. 
#zarascenes #zara 
Starring @micarganaraz
Photography director @wabizabi 
Stylist @mr_carlos_nazario
Hair @jimmypaulhair
Make-up @erinparsonsmakeup

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by ZARA Official on August 02, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text:
JOIN LIFE. We are working to make both our physical and online stores increasingly more sustainable. To this end, we are developing specific programs to design, build and manage our stores efficiently and with a lower environmental impact. Our goal is that by 2022, 10% of the energy in all our headquarters logistics centres and stores will come from renewable sources 
#JOINLIFE

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by ZARA Official on August 02, 2021. May be an image of one or more people.

node.text:
JOIN LIFE. Under the label Join Life we categorize all garments that have been produced using processes and raw materials that help us reduce our environmental impact. Our goal is that by 2022, 50% of our products will meet our Join Life standard.  
#JOINLIFE

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by ZARA Official on August 02, 2021. May be a closeup of 1 person.

node.text:
JOIN LIFE. Working towards sustainability. 

At Zara, we understand sustainability as an ongoing effort. We develop specific programs from a holistic approach. Emphasizing social and environmental sustainability and the safety and health of our products. 
#JOINLIFE

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by ZARA Official on July 27, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text:
Studio Issue 001. 
Drawing inspiration from the evocative and timeless carrés, this sophisticated collection uses a selection of natural silk twill scarves to create a limited edition of artfully cut pieces. 
The combination of different print and motives emphasizes the lightness and the movement of these designs. 
#zarawoman
